These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different games are played: poker, whist
1. the person playing poker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Game   | whist | poker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: british, colombian
1. the colombian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |
| Nationality   | british | colombian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, lily
1. the person who growslily is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | lily |

 #################################

 
